title: Nickelodeon Commercials From The 1990's
description:
I spent a good bit of time downloading these individually, as I grew exhausted of editing compilation clips. Inspired by Nick Reboot, I decided to do the same thing on my local machine but soon realized that without the commercials, it just wasn't the same.

So here's 70 commercials from the 90's ranging from toys to cereal. Most of which are in good quality. I tried to avoid VHS rips as much as I could
